{
  "sections": {
    "gp_section_614274111069225643": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "ca3b520546e9225c9a3743d711719d19d74e93a3d4a85b5a22e64db0fde4b76b_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg-S4VGxDgN_text": "<p>Per shoe</p>",
        "ggDmZnDPKWD_text": "<p>460g</p>",
        "ggV9jI-Hp0z_text": "<p>Certified</p>",
        "gg_JQFHE7Dl_text": "<p>Per shoe</p>",
        "gghdpIsJUBw_text": "<p>S3</p>",
        "ggqDlmBv8Tu_text": "<p>Workers switched</p>",
        "ggsZTcPMoOB_text": "<p>&nbsp;Gel insoles. Frozen water bottles. Calf &nbsp;stretches &nbsp;before every shift. Maybe even a &nbsp;podiatrist at &nbsp;£50 a visit.<br><br><strong>&nbsp;It still comes back every morning.</strong> Because &nbsp;these fixes treat the symptom, not what's &nbsp;causing the damage 8 hours a day.</p>",
        "ggu2prWUZL5_text": "<p>15,000+</p>",
        "ggzv0NWxZvN_text": "<p>460g</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-614274111069225643"
    },
    "gp_section_614274113300595504": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "ed57c7626616da7fccdd150e910dd6a61290d0bd2b95efe21cd649e64d5d347f_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggdBep49_gL_text": "5 Gründe, warum Ihre Sicherheitsschuhe Ihre Plantarfasziitis <span style=\"color:#FFD706;\"><i>verschlimmern</i></span>",
        "ggdCTPDPq2P_text": "<p>If that first step out of bed feels like standing on broken glass, your boots aren't just failing you.&nbsp;</p><p><i><strong>They're the reason it's getting worse.</strong></i></p>",
        "section_preload": "true"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-614274113300595504"
    },
    "gp_section_614274127276016432": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "78cc2c9f72f7e84438845e5658dbc1f88354beb0e9890cade22b50449e6c2460_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg-wD6fL1OU_text": "1.Every step in a 1kg boot is a hammer blow to your fascia",
        "gg4uMW1S-SV_text": "1.Every step in a 1kg boot is a hammer blow to your fascia",
        "gg5w1plgG8A_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/85ee055ec2004025bc00091145ecaa9a.mp4",
        "gg5w1plgG8A_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/1095883398",
        "gg5w1plgG8A_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NfASaHFN1zg",
        "ggO6rpANfnk_text": "<p>The average safety boot weighs over 1kg per foot. On a standard shift, that's somewhere between 8,000 and 12,000 steps: <strong>8 to 12 tonnes of extra load</strong> your plantar fascia absorbs every day compared to a lighter shoe.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Your fascia is a thin band of tissue. It wasn't built for that kind of repeated impact on concrete. Over months, it develops micro-tears faster than your body can repair them. That's when the stabbing pain starts.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-614274127276016432"
    },
    "gp_section_614274127326347947": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "739c29432a21e49b216df5099f34c22e8c9fce7ae78bc3e28154c43bf6d9cafe_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg1_4NUgnj__text": "<p><span style=\"color:#666666;\">14 years on the tools and I just accepted it, sore feet, that's the job. Never thought to question the boots themselves. Changed pairs about six weeks ago and the difference in how my feet feel at the end of the day is night and day. Genuinely annoyed I didn't do it sooner.</span></p>",
        "gg9ji1OFTqM_alt": "Alt Image",
        "gg9ji1OFTqM_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/CREA_1080X1080_-_2026-04-02T150437.435.png",
        "gg9ji1OFTqM_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/CREA_1080X1080_-_2026-04-02T150437.435.png",
        "gg9ji1OFTqM_title": "Image Title",
        "ggV8ikQvsod_text": "2.Steel sole plates lock your arch in the worst possible position",
        "gg_TUrWv5-O_text": "2.Steel sole plates lock your arch in the worst possible position",
        "ggaREXpRe_G_alt": "Alt Image",
        "ggaREXpRe_G_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://ucarecdn.com/c90e5b61-8513-4914-9c30-40a1950282e2/-/format/auto/",
        "ggaREXpRe_G_title": "Image Title",
        "ggdDdnaHZ_Y_text": "<p>Traditional safety boots use a steel anti-puncture plate in the sole, not the toe cap, the plate underneath your foot. It stops nails going through. But it also <strong>stops your foot from flexing naturally.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Your arch is designed to load and unload with every step, distributing pressure evenly. A steel plate forces it flat, concentrating all the pressure on the exact spot where the fascia connects to the heel bone. Exactly where it hurts most.</p>",
        "ggkl2BZ47Mv_text": "<p><strong>Oliver S.</strong> <span style=\"color:#B4B4B4;font-size:13px;\">/ Site Electrician</span></p>",
        "ggrX1DVYfz0_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/8383803caf584b75a53902ab94df1050.mp4",
        "ggrX1DVYfz0_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/1095883398",
        "ggrX1DVYfz0_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NfASaHFN1zg"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-614274127326347947"
    },
    "gp_section_614274145546404507": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "b316b8b4012c8f955140834fcf20d295b99143ad5e3472317de67d0323ba3d22_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggATNxofyZU_alt": "Alt Image",
        "ggATNxofyZU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/CREA_1080X1080_-_2026-04-02T150453.103.png",
        "ggATNxofyZU_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/hh2.webp",
        "ggATNxofyZU_title": "Image Title",
        "ggF53NiOgL5_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/1bc4ec9c2aae47139d2629e6238e0e39.mp4",
        "ggF53NiOgL5_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/1095883398",
        "ggF53NiOgL5_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NfASaHFN1zg",
        "ggPQd6HnHra_text": "5.Plantar fasciitis doesn't stay the same — it gets worse",
        "ggY57V1jUSR_text": "<p><strong>Steve</strong> <span style=\"color:#B4B4B4;font-size:13px;\">/ Groundworker</span></p>",
        "ggcDxiPU9mI_text": "5.Plantar fasciitis doesn't stay the same: it gets worse",
        "ggf58v638WC_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#666666;\">Worst part wasn't the pain at work, you sort of get used to that. Worst part was getting home and not being able to do anything. Sat on the sofa like an old man at 34. That's what made me actually do something about it. Three weeks later and I'm back walking the dog after work. Small thing but it meant a lot.</span></p>",
        "ggpvg2rf53Q_alt": "Alt Image",
        "ggpvg2rf53Q_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://ucarecdn.com/c90e5b61-8513-4914-9c30-40a1950282e2/-/format/auto/",
        "ggpvg2rf53Q_title": "Image Title",
        "ggv4x9MGu-1_text": "<p>PF is progressive. The micro-tears multiply. Scar tissue builds up. The pain that used to fade by mid-morning starts lasting all day. <strong>By midday, you're limping. By end of shift, every step is agony.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The longer you spend in boots that don't support your foot properly, the harder it becomes to reverse.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-614274145546404507"
    },
    "gp_section_614274145546404654": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "150e28e44d560234adf079d562388a1abda440c1a00d6fc9e159118bb1f5ac18_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggHjbrthALf_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/section4.webp",
        "ggJi_VktR8Z_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/Rectangle_41017.png",
        "ggJi_VktR8Z_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/section4.webp",
        "ggeImyurq77_text": "3.Concrete kills your boots from the inside and your feet pay for it",
        "ggf2g_IL2mT_text": "<p>Concrete draws moisture out of leather, it's why concrete always feels cold underfoot. Over weeks, this dries and hardens the leather in your boots. <strong>The cushioning degrades. The structure stiffens.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>By the time your boots feel \"broken in,\" they've already lost most of the shock absorption your feet need. And replacing them every few months isn't realistic.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-614274145546404654"
    },
    "gp_section_614274145563181872": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "6c40aa8a9574290b7fc19260a7c3f4838a92c8c084cbaa10fefaa724809c37dc_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg1NLANU1L-_text": "<p>Gel insoles, frozen water bottles, calf stretches, podiatrist visits. They help for an hour. Maybe two. <strong>Then you go back to standing on concrete in a rigid, heavy boot and the damage starts again.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It's like icing a bruise every night and hitting the same spot with a hammer every morning.</p>",
        "ggBC7g7cIRI_text": "<p><strong>Emma C.</strong> <span style=\"color:#B4B4B4;font-size:13px;\">/ Warehouse Supervisor</span></p>",
        "ggTX0Y-hcWs_text": "4.Insoles and ice don't fix the thing that's causing the damage",
        "ggYAK6JIOZT_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/Rectangle_41017.png",
        "ggYAK6JIOZT_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/1775132374154-019d4e22-443a-733f-b8ea-79f4f69fd892.png",
        "ggaLPa1bT96_alt": "Alt Image",
        "ggaLPa1bT96_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://ucarecdn.com/c90e5b61-8513-4914-9c30-40a1950282e2/-/format/auto/",
        "ggaLPa1bT96_title": "Image Title",
        "ggkm12eXF17_alt": "Alt Image",
        "ggkm12eXF17_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/CREA_1080X1080_-_2026-04-02T150443.894.png",
        "ggkm12eXF17_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/CREA_1080X1080_-_2026-04-02T150443.894.png",
        "ggkm12eXF17_title": "Image Title",
        "ggoeopNzR4U_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/1775132374154-019d4e22-443a-733f-b8ea-79f4f69fd892.png",
        "ggzeulTqr-D_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#666666;\">Must have spent £300-400 over the years on different things to sort my feet out. Appointments, products, you name it. Turned out the answer was simpler than all of that. A mate on site said just change what you're wearing 8 hours a day. Obvious when someone says it out loud.</span></p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-614274145563181872"
    },
