        "gg3sFvYlDgO_text": "<p>S3 certification requires specific performance standards, not a specific material. Solydia uses a Kevlar anti-puncture plate instead of steel.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Lighter, and it allows your foot to flex naturally instead of being locked rigid.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The result: 460 grams per shoe with deep heel cushioning and proper arch support built for 8+ hours on concrete.</p>",
        "ggIFNnxD6uB_childItem_0": "<p>460g per shoe</p>",
