        "ggdRXcV3Nwk_text": "So what actually works?",
        "gge5fjg9i8t_text": "<p>Traditional Boot</p>",
        "ggeznjlcDJI_text": "<p>Full S3 protection, without the weight and rigidity that's destroying your fascia.</p>",
